column3:
Add compose Gradle extension to dependency blocks

Before this change, the following Groovy DSL code would not work:
```
dependency {
  implementation compose.desktop.currentOS
}

// or

kotlin {
    jvm { withJava() }
    sourceSets {
        named("jvmMain") {
            dependencies {
                implementation(compose.desktop.currentOs)
            }
        }
    }
}
```

